for dataset in datasets.keys():
    datasets[dataset].obsm['X_pca'] = sc.tl.pca(datasets[dataset].layers['normalised'], n_comps=3, random_state=40)
    sc.pl.pca(datasets[dataset], projection='2d', color='branch', title = f'{dataset}_Branches', palette = Simulation_pal,size=30)
